<TITLE>
Nukumi, the Micmac grandmother (Nokumi, Nogami)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Nukumi (Nogami,)
a wise grandmother from the folklore of the Mi'kmaq tribe.">
